  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Car
    Car Subclass to vehicle, includes length of cars used for transporting and number of doors.
    Ferry
    Ferry Subclass to Transport, a ferry capable of loading cars onto its ramp and moving them around.
    Saab95
    Subclass to Car, always creates the same car, set amount of doors, power etc.
    Scania
    Scania Subclass to car, includes a ramp which can be raised and lowered between 0 and 70 degrees.
    Trailer
    Trailer Subclass to transport, a trailer able to load and unload cars from its ramp and move them around.
    Transport
    Transport Subclass to vehicle, capable of loading cars (excluding Scania) onto its ramp and moving them around.
    Vehicle
    Vehicle The abstract Vehicle class is the superclass for the whole project, handling subclasses such as Transport and Car.

    Tests Various tests, checking every method and its usability.
    Volvo240
